displayProperties.name: Gauntlet's Chosen
displayProperties.description: Return to Lord Saladin.
Return to Eva in the Tower and purchase a Contender Card using your Laurels.

Equip your Guardian Games Class item. Then collect Laurels by defeating minibosses, or lesser enemies with your Grenades, Melee attacks, or Supers.

You have a chance to earn bonus progress when you pick up Laurels that match your class.  The new Guardian Games Strike Playlist is a great place to start!
